200.html:
created_at

date-time

Creation timestamp of the client token.

created_by_handle

string

Handle of the user who created the client token.

created_by_uuid

uuid

UUID of the user who created the client token.

disabled_at

date-time

Timestamp when the client token was disabled.

disabled_by

int64

ID of the user who disabled the client token.

disabled_by_handle

string

Handle of the user who disabled the client token.

hash

string

The hash value of the client token. This is the secret token value that should be used in your browser or mobile application.

modified_by

int64

ID of the user who last modified the client token.

name

string

Name of the client token.

org_id

int64

Organization ID associated with the client token.

origin_urls [required]

[string]

List of allowed origin URLs for browser-based applications. Requests from URLs not in this list will be rejected.
